= Calendar Plugin for Rails =
========
===  Install ===
	{{{
		script/plugin install http://calendarplugin.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/
	}}}

===  Usage ===
	{{{
		<%=calendar_field :user,:birthday%>
	}}}
	
	* The default language is en,if you want to use chinese,use
	{{{
			<%=calendar_field :user,:birthday,{:lang=>'zh_CN'}%>
	}}}
	
	* The default size of text input is 12,if you want to change it,use
	{{{
			<%=calendar_field :user,:birthday,{:size=>12}%>
	}}}
	
	* The default data format is '%Y-%m-%d',if you want to change it,use
	{{{
			<%=calendar_field :user,:birthday,{:date_format=>'%Y-%m-%d'}%>
	}}}	
	
	* The default skin is aqua,if you want to change it ,use
	{{{
			<%=calendar_field :user,:birthday,{:skin=>'aqua'}%>
	}}}		
	
	* More complex example
	{{{
			<%=calendar_field :user,:birthday,{:size=>8,:lang=>'zh_CN',:skin=>'aqua'}%>
	}}}			